  "title": "Senior Interior Designer (commercial office)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Consult and collaborate with Design Director in all design concepts</li><li>Take ownership in all the projects assigned by Design Director and Office Manager</li><li>Developing outstanding design and detailing in every project</li><li>Good communication with clients to correctly interpret and document what they want in their requirements</li><li>Responsible for the output and quality of the design documentation</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced, ever-changing and high-pressure environment</li><li>Complete a full project from scratch independently</li><li>Working in the field for at least 5 years and with site experience</li><li>Possess excellence space planning skill</li><li>Well verse in Power Point, Excel, Words, AutoCAD, Sketch-Up, Photoshop</li><li>Possess team spirit with good interpersonal skill</li><li>Possess FF&E knowledge</li><li>Familiar with Local Building/Construction/Fire Safety Code</li><li>Construction drawings and detail drawings</li><li>Able to travel</li><li>Good presentation skill</li></ul>",
